000, 12 433 600 PYRS, and 1 059.86 PYRS/100 000, respectively. All the aboved 
indicators were declined from 1990 to 2010, in 2010 they were 3 065 985 800 
cases, 224 351.66 cases/100 000, 388 600 cases, 30.74 cases/100 000, 19 492 200 
