mortality, mortality rate, DALY, DALY rate, YLL, YLL rate, YLD, and YLD rate 
were 56.84%, -9.85%, -33.07%, -61.54%, -27.68%, -58.42%, -32.46%, -61.17%, 
-16.75%, and -52.13% for 50-69 age group; for ≥ 70 age group, 57.90%, -5.86%, 
7.41%, -36.12%, -5.00%, -43.51%, -5.14%, -43.59%, -4.52%, and -43.2%.
CONCLUSIONS: The burden of infectious disease of the Chinese population was 
declined from 1990 to 2010; however, the incidence of infectious disease was 
increased in ≥ 50 age groups.

